						<div class="postbody">Start is easier to hit during action sequences than select, which is why it's often mapped to a third command.<br /><br />Kinda funny, the AVGN lists the &quot;Seven Deadly Sins&quot; of game design in his Kid Kool ree-view <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5BqCAOGRR2Q" class="postlink">link</a>. And yes, one complaint is uncontrollable jumps <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" /></div>

